---
title: Sun-Dried Tomato Focaccia Serves 2 | with Olives
description: Focaccia comes together in no time with pre-made pizza dough. This verison is studded with olives and sun-dried tomato pesto for the perfect pasta side!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sun-dried-tomato-focaccia-5484725c-49bdf628.jpg
